title: Marina divided on proposed medical-marijuana store
text:
Photo: Leah Millis, The Chronicle A pedestrian walks past the proposed future site for a new medical cannabis dispensary called The Apothecarium off of Lombard Street Oct. 20, 2015 in San Francisco, Calif. A pedestrian walks past the proposed future site for a new medical...
Nearly 15 years after San Francisco’s first legal pot dispensaries rolled up in neighborhoods like the Castro and South of Market, the Marina district is buzzing over a proposal to plant a medical marijuana outlet on busy Lombard Street.
